text: Maxyutovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Ilchimbetovsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 45 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Tuymazy, 12 km from Ilchimbetovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Maxyutovo, Tuymazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
